    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for the overview. i guess i'm wondering more about the 'critics' part. i've heard some people saying that these lessons are actually harmful or even bad for kids' development. is that a widespread view, or is it just some small group of people being difficult? like, is there a scientific basis for what they're worried about?",
